data.description: NEW PRICE!!  SAME GREAT HOUSE!!  Welcome to this charming home in the desirable Pasadena Estates!  Upon entry, beautiful Italian tile flooring greets you, along with windows that allow plenty of natural sunlight.  The first-floor level includes 2 bedrooms and 1 bathroom situated off the front room.  The kitchen area then flows to a large storage area with a washer and dryer hookup and then to the large insulated sunroom located at the back of the home.    The highlight of this home is the complete second level, which serves as the primary suite and third bedroom. With its own full-size en-suite bathroom and loads of closet space, including a spacious 8x5 extra closet nook area that can be used for dressing, sitting, working, or indoor bar area, you decide!  With plenty of options, the primary suite offers privacy and a retreat-like atmosphere.    Another unique feature of this house is the insulated sunroom on the lower level, providing a versatile space to enjoy year-round. Whether you want to relax, entertain guests, or use it as a home office or workout room, this sunroom will surely be a favorite spot in the house.    Convenience is key with alley access, allowing easy entry and exit from the property. The backyard is large enough to accommodate a boat or RV, providing ample space for outdoor recreational vehicles or even a swimming pool to cool down in during those hot Florida Summers!    Come and explore this wonderful home that offers both comfort and functionality. Don't miss out on this opportunity to make it your own!
